    "answer_id" : 42113885,
    "question_id" : 12912287,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Add a live template called \"ser\" to the other group, set it to \"Applicable in Java: declaration\", and untick \"Shorten FQ names\". Give it a template text of just:</p>\n\n<pre><code>$serial$\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Now edit variables and set serial to:</p>\n\n<pre><code>groovyScript(\"(System.env.JDK_HOME+'/bin/serialver -classpath '+com.intellij.openapi.fileEditor.FileDocumentManager.instance.getFile(_editor.document).path.replaceAll('/java/.*','').replaceAll('/src/','/build/classes/')+' '+_1).execute().text.replaceAll('.*: *','')\",qualifiedClassName())\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>It assumes the standard Gradle project layout. Change /build/ to /target/ for Maven.</p>\n"
