    "question_id" : 12912287,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Without any plugins: You just need to enable highlight in IntelliJ:</p>\n\n<p><code>IntelliJ Preferences -&gt; Editor -&gt; Inspections -&gt; Java -&gt; Serialization issues -&gt; Serializable class without 'serialVersionUID'</code> - set flag and click <code>'OK'</code>.</p>\n\n<p>Now, if your class implements <code>Serializable</code>, you will see highlight, and <code>alt+Enter</code> on class name will propose to generate <code>private static final long serialVersionUID</code>.</p>\n\n<p>PS: Taken from <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/24573643/how-to-generate-serial-version-uid-in-intellij/36007392#36007392\">here</a></p>\n"
  }, {
