    "body" : "<p>With version <code>v2018.2.1</code></p>\n\n<p>Go to </p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>Preference > Editor > Inspections > Java > Serialization issues > toggle \"Serializable class without 'serialVersionUID'\".</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>A warning should appear next to the class declaration.</p>\n"
