      "reputation" : 11829,
      "user_id" : 5889131,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 100,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/S0TUH.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "jeremysprofile",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/5889131/jeremysprofile"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 23,
    "last_activity_date" : 1588787167,
    "creation_date" : 1588787167,
    "answer_id" : 61641757,
    "question_id" : 12912287,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Easiest modern method: <code>Alt</code>+<code>Enter</code> on</p>\n\n<pre><code>private static final long serialVersionUID = ;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>IntelliJ will underline the space after the <code>=</code>. put your cursor on it and hit <code>alt</code>+<code>Enter</code> (<code>Option</code>+<code>Enter</code> on Mac). You'll get a popover that says \"Randomly Change serialVersionUID Initializer\". Just hit enter, and it'll populate that space with a random long. </p>\n"
  }, {
